UNITY3D

2D GAME

Development
-  No double jumps through OverlapCircle and LayerMask
- Trail pulsation LineRenderer
- Unions by SprintJoint2D for building objects connectedAnchor is the point pressed on the screen, while for objects that you collect the connectedAnchor is pj own.

